If "<Hdr$Path>"="" Then Error AcornC/C++ Tools not yet opened
|
If "<pd_root>"<>""  Then Error 0 Please reboot and reselect
|
| SKS RISC PC
If "<disc_root>"="" Then IfThere ADFS::id0.$.!Boot Then Set disc_root ADFS::id0.$
|
| SKS iMX6
If "<disc_root>"="" Then IfThere SCSI::hd4.$.!Boot Then Set disc_root SCSI::hd4.$
|
| Raspberry Pi
If "<disc_root>"="" Then IfThere SDFS::RISCOSpi.$.!Boot Then Set disc_root SDFS::RISCOSpi.$
|
| RPCEmu
If "<disc_root>"="" Then IfThere HostFS:$.!Boot Then Set disc_root HostFS:$
|
If "<disc_root>"="" Then Error 0 Please locate root disc
|
Set pd_root <disc_root>.pipedream.trunk
|
Unset disc_root
|
URD <pd_root>
|Lib &.arm.library
Dir &.pd
|
Set PipeDream$ReportEnable 1
Set PipeDream$TraceEnable 1
|
Filer_OpenDir <Obey$Dir>.r32
|
| end of !!!Boot
